{"tid":347673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬鞍山路恐怖車禍　拖車司機被撞劏肚","createTime":"2017-08-05T04:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T07:06:16.000Z","uid":12705,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"032a37149b32c2601b75e7d20ddaa1bd366e4004","tid":347673,"uid":12705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T04:35:10.000Z","msg":"沙田發生恐佈交通意外，拖車司機被撞劏肚。今晨7時許，一輛私家車沿馬鞍山路快線往馬鞍山方向行駛，至石門附近香港海關車輛扣留中心對開失事撞壆，右邊前後車胎爆裂，遂停在快線及召拖車協助。稍後一輛拖車到場停在私家車前，拖車司機站在兩車中間工作，不料一輛七人車尾隨駛至，竟企圖由拖車右邊與路肩之間空位穿過，期間將拖車司機撞倒，他慘被夾在兩車中間拖行，右腹更被拖車鐵架劏開，部份腸臟溢出，警員接報到場，立即召救護車將其送院搶救。[red]而爆胎私家車司機接受酒精呼氣測試證實超標，涉嫌酒後駕駛連同肇事七人車司機一同被捕。 <br />\n<br />\n七人車司機真係on99<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170805/mobile/bkn-20170805085435760-0805_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170805%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170805085435760-0805_00822_001.html&d=Ojd2XZwUuNL6cbgivLjUcbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=626d23c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170805/mobile/bkn-20170805085435760-0805_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d522070d60d3aad8188a2fc36ada84deb42b228c","tid":347673,"uid":73281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T04:47:37.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"42f583af613c1e372ce314f0f8a706857f2a1498","tid":347673,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T04:48:10.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"23585fb393db2eb13e071919f4c408f5e0b5e4f1","tid":347673,"uid":70505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:21:06.000Z","msg":"弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f44854509bcef768d837ef5c1767802f0631881","tid":347673,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T06:21:45.000Z","msg":"講還講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3fa60ef3627633030a55d988f710ae73fbcbf4","tid":347673,"uid":51294,"like":0,"